Reasoning: 
- cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing) is the most likely category as the paper discusses scheduling tasks in a cloud-based computing system. 
- cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) is also likely as the paper mentions a cloud-based video streaming engine and QoS metrics. 
- cs.MM (Multimedia) is another possible category as the paper focuses on processing video streaming tasks. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is a potential category as the paper proposes a mechanism to improve the robustness of the system. 
- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) is also a possible category as the paper discusses identifying and aggregating mergeable tasks.
